---
title: Quick Creamy Chicken & Veggies with Mashed Potato
description: Something magical happens when you combine this decadent creamy sauce with diced chicken and veggies, then pile it on a chive mash potato. It all comes together so beautifully, you'll be wanting to lick the plate clean!

*Unfortunately, this
week's baby broccoli
was in short supply, so
we've replaced it with
courgette. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
